## 🎯 Elevator Pitch (Memorize This)

> **"Real-Hero is an AI-powered blood donation platform built with React, Node.js, MongoDB, and Python FastAPI. It uses geospatial queries to find nearby eligible donors, ML models to predict acceptance probability and blood shortages, and a 3-layer notification system — email, web push, and in-app — to alert the right donors at the right time. Gamification features like Hero Points and loyalty tiers keep the donor community engaged. The system has 8 ML models, 14 backend routes, 20 frontend pages, and 11 database collections — a production-grade, full-stack capstone project."**

