## 📌 TCS Digital Interview Tips

| Tip | Why It Matters |
|---|---|
| **Lead with impact**, not technology | TCS values business problem understanding |
| **Know your algorithms by name** | "Logistic Regression", "Holt-Winters" — not just "some ML model" |
| **Mention tradeoffs** | Why MongoDB over SQL? Why FastAPI for ML? Shows design thinking |
| **Be honest about limitations** | Interviewers respect self-awareness |
| **Prepare a 30-second and 3-minute version** of your explanation | They may ask "briefly explain" or "explain in detail" |
| **Know your code** | They may ask you to write pseudocode for donor matching or OTP flow |
| **Use numbers** | "11 models", "14 routes", "8 ML endpoints" — specifics impress interviewers |
